Home / News Budget / Taxes / NOTICE TO READERS: Incorrect date for public hearing on tax increment financing in St. Paul NOTICE TO READERS: Incorrect date for public hearing on tax increment financing in St. Paul By: admin October 15, 2015 0 
The notice of public hearing regarding the adoption of a tax increment financing plan for the Wabasha and Sixth Street Tax Increment Financing District in the Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, edition of The St. Paul Legal Ledger â€” Capitol Report inadvertently appeared with an incorrect meeting date. The hearing has not occurred yet and the correct meeting date will be published at a later date. We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused.
